OL,5, Ministers have drawn up large benefit  
OL,6, changes for people who are unable to   
OL,7, work due to health conditions, the BBC 
OL,8, has learned.                           
OL,10,FThe changes, affecting hundreds of     
OL,11,Fthousands of people from 2025, would   
OL,12,Fsave #4bn from the welfare budget.     
OL,14,FThe proposals would see many more      
OL,15,Fpeople forced to find work despite     
OL,16,Fsuffering from a range of physical and 
OL,17,Fmental health conditions.              
OL,19,FThe Department for Work and Pensions   
OL,20,Fsaid reform would be gradual.          
